{"tid":1246593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住一陣唔好用八達通，用散紙搭車！！！","createTime":"2019-06-20T19:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T04:46:50.000Z","uid":28914,"like":384,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"bd0e9fc4761e1bc6c379aaeacc98b5f1b9875162","tid":1246593,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:10:11.000Z","msg":"1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Disable Finger Print / Face Unlock 基本啦。</span></strong><br />\n如果好似之前咁一落車就俾狗圍，最緊要唔好驚，老虎蟹都唔可以俾佢惡到你解鎖部機。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺之前 《楊政賢案》(HCAL 122/2014) 高院已經頒下判詞： <br />\n94. (1). On a proper construction, in relation to the digital content of a mobile phone (or a similar device) seized on arrest, section 50(6) authorizes police officers to search it without warrant only in exigent circumstances. <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第94段 (1) 「在非緊急情況下，《警察條例》第50(6)<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">並沒有</span></span>授權警員可以在無搜查令的情況下搜查市民的電子設備，包括手提電話、手提電腦、平版電腦、甚至智能手錶。」 </span></strong>(自己翻譯，法律朋友唔該幫手check check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔該你地同我背咗佢，到時有理有據就唔洗驚！！</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記住Disable 埋手機定位服務！ ！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可以嘅話，用太空卡<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(唔好用CSL！！)</span>/後備電話</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n4. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人多網絡一定差，Download 定 Firechat 定以防萬一！！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.opengarden.com/firechat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opengarden.com%2Ffirechat%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4raniVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=c0d0d85e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.opengarden.com/firechat/</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時淨係諗到咁多，請各位補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5670afe8329591b01becfd52057cfdbdc50733","tid":1246593,"uid":28914,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:11:30.000Z","msg":"推到七點為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819cbd8c48ee01d543ef6330b767814525601fdb","tid":1246593,"uid":28914,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:11:57.000Z","msg":"推到七點為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a2aacc40c96167b33de4d457ba82210e30af55","tid":1246593,"uid":28914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:12:14.000Z","msg":"推到七點為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afaae85ab5736ddbdb047894fe99d4f417a8fa29","tid":1246593,"uid":205191,"like":4,"dislike":80,"score":-76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:15:04.000Z","msg":"聽日準備有花生食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab2e0f008a82c4fb9539917c6a2b1a074bab3c2","tid":1246593,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5268a4e5ddf369f9b17bcffaf9396b798e7432","tid":1246593,"uid":28914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:15:39.000Z","msg":"推到七點為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60be4ceedea75edeedefe51726311401d2db871c","tid":1246593,"uid":28914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201