,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:23:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2205e5b146fe853727c8dd7f3ee7ac52aa227233","tid":1246593,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:27:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5d1d4518ec6e183a4e8c033f3ad3d5326fd4d2a","tid":1246593,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:32:42.000Z","msg":"推到八點為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b4eb03ad1eedf08568e4af945982015ee5cc57","tid":1246593,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:33:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06e81eeb8b1cb22ce496561d16f6ba5c31ddb866","tid":1246593,"uid":63808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:36:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dccd17b381cd9213638270506db9791e4fa057c7","tid":1246593,"uid":235080,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"bd0e9fc4761e1bc6c379aaeacc98b5f1b9875162","tid":1246593,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:10:11.000Z","msg":"1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Disable Finger Print / Face Unlock 基本啦。</span></strong><br />\n如果好似之前咁一落車就俾狗圍，最緊要唔好驚，老虎蟹都唔可以俾佢惡到你解鎖部機。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺之前 《楊政賢案》(HCAL 122/2014) 高院已經頒下判詞： <br />\n94. (1). On a proper construction, in relation to the digital content of a mobile phone (or a similar device) seized on arrest, section 50(6) authorizes police officers to search it without warrant only in exigent circumstances. <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第94段 (1) 「在非緊急情況下，《警察條例》第50(6)<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">並沒有</span></span>授權警員可以在無搜查令的情況下搜查市民的電子設備，包括手提電話、手提電腦、平版電腦、甚至智能手錶。」 </span></strong>(自己翻